Name: Population growth rate
Description: This type holds data about the population growth rate of different locations, expressed as a percentage change between two dates.

Properties.Name: Date one
Properties.Description: The first date for which population was measured for this comparison.

Properties.Name: Date two
Properties.Description: The final date for which population was measured for this comparison.

Properties.Name: Percent growth
Properties.Description: The percent growth (negative numbers mean a population decrease) of this location over this period.
